PN,39301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779030723
OL,3,CManchester City win the FA Cup
OL,5,FManchester City kept alive their hopes
OL,6,Fof winning a domestic treble as
OL,7,FAntoine Semenyo's sensational second-
OL,8,Fhalf finish broke Chelsea's resolve to
OL,9,Fsettle the FA Cup final 1-0 at Wembley.
OL,11,FCity's attentions now turn to the
OL,12,FPremier League title race and
OL,13,FBournemouth away on Tuesday.
OL,15,FIf this is to be Pep Guardiola's final
OL,16,Fseason in charge, he will bow out with
OL,17,Fat least two trophies following the
OL,18,FCarabao Cup win here in March.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
