PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779030723
OL,3,CManchester City win the FA Cup
OL,5,FChelsea succeeded in making the first
OL,6,Fhalf one of little spectacle, their
OL,7,Fback five stifling City and robbing
OL,8,Fthem of space in which to play.
OL,10,FIndeed there were almost no chances in
OL,11,Fthe opening period. One came when
OL,12,FChelsea passed themselves into a mess
OL,13,Fin the right-back position. Reece
OL,14,FJames, receiving the ball under
OL,15,Fpressure, was barged off it by
OL,16,FHaaland, who carried it into the box
OL,17,Fand fizzed across goal to no one.
OL,19,FHaaland then put the ball in the net
OL,20,Ffrom a cross by Matheus Nunes who had
OL,21,Fstrayed offside before delivering.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779030723
OL,3,CManchester City win the FA Cup
OL,5,FGuardiola was unhappy that Fernandez
OL,6,Fescaped with a yellow card for what
OL,7,Flooked a two-footed challenge on Silva
OL,8,Fbefore Haaland finally had the game's
OL,9,Ffirst serious attempt in the 43rd
OL,10,Fminute, getting in behind Wesley
OL,11,FFofana and firing straight at Sanchez.
OL,13,FIt was not a surprise to see the
OL,14,Fineffective Omar Marmoush withdrawn at
OL,15,Fhalf-time, with Rayan Cherki on to try
OL,16,Fand finally punch a hole in Chelsea's
OL,17,Frearguard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779030723
OL,3,CManchester City win the FA Cup
OL,5,FSemenyo ought to have put City in
OL,6,Ffront two minutes after the break but
OL,7,Fheaded Nico O'Reilly's excellent cross
OL,8,Finches over.
OL,10,FA stolid final looked increasingly
OL,11,Flike an individual moment would decide
OL,12,Fit and from nothing one arrived in the
OL,13,F72nd minute. Haaland's cross was
OL,14,Fperfectly pitched and Semenyo's flick
OL,15,Ffinally breached Chelsea's defence.
OL,17,FFernandez almost replied instantly,
OL,18,Fflicking Colwill's header on to the
OL,19,Froof of James Trafford's goal. It was
OL,20,Fa glorious chance to level the final
OL,21,Fand Chelsea would not get another.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
