PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779030723
OL,3,CManchester City win the FA Cup
OL,5,FCherki was denied by a flying save
OL,6,Ffrom Sanchez after Chelsea gave the
OL,7,Fball away again in their own third. A
OL,8,Fsecond goal would have more fairly
OL,9,Freflected City's superiority.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
